Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make sure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:15.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Phantom Lord guild came to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza defended against the Magic Focusing Cannon, Jupiter, and she was knocked out of commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're infiltrating Phantom's guild in order to destroy the cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:36.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:47.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:58.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:05.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:10.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:18.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:30.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:35.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:38.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:41.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:46.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter has activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, that's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never eaten fire like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you're the Dragon Slayer I've heard rumors about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we're both at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire won't work on either of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go decidin' that yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even hit you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! I can't be hit by fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon's... {I'm switching the usual order in order to preserve the joke... Call it an exception}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All fire is under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So No One Sees the Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,2 minutes until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter's gonna fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:58.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see? I {\i1}eat{\i0} fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That fire's the smell of a mop drenched with curdled milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You dirty little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,1 minute until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there... Giving up on magic and using your fists?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case I, with my katana, have the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A scratch like that can't destroy such a large lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you don't learn a thing, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, that... He expanded the fire enough so I'd get hit by it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 30 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking Natsu so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,20 second until Jupiter fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already... All fire is under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:35.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That fire... It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's resisting my control?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he figure that out {\i1}during{\i0} the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you move {\i1}my{\i0} fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter as long as you don't hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:57.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aimin' for you from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:16.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They managed to destroy Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:31.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire ain't gonna listen to people telling it what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It responds to your heart's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without defeating him and overcoming his control of fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been impossible to destroy Jupiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was the one who wasn't thinking calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad there, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without Jupiter, we'll manage things somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance to push them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe out the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bratty children got their spunk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start up the giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't manipulate my fire any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:09.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn to get blown to smithereens, Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stabilizing elements!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating lateral balance lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizards in dangerous areas, evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It awakens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tilting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This area isn't laterally stabilized!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laterally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what are they planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hip joints stabilized! Standing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant has awakened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant... A magical giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should grovel and beg for forgiveness, you damn kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will learn your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feast on despair until the end of your pitiful lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shades are coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant and ghosts? What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll concentrate on the Shades!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Natsu will find a way to stop the giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and transportation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You get motion sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat fire as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll burn you to a crisp with my strongest magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you to bits, Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:55.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...fly to the heavens and become a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Natsu is so pitiful, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:16.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, then {\i1}you{\i0} should make the {\i1}car{\i0} sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are these the remains of Jupiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stopped all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a look outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Letters? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic circle is for Abyss Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the forbidden magics!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At that size, we're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:47.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnolia itself will be destroyed in the wave of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what they said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to split up and find the power moving this giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Out of the frying pan and into the fire....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira, how long until that magic spell activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About 10 minutes, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to destroy its power source somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:16.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our men inside must be thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There're people other than Natsu in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray and Elfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? He also wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Elfman can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped us when we raided them before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:38.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting with their lackeys is one thing, but if he goes up against their big guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As he is now, Elfman can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:49.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, you, Elfman, and everyone too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all suffered a deep wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in his own way, he's forced himself to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you realize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman... moved forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have to move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are looking for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your attack on the guild this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This should at least buy everyone some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that Lucy wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How powerless am I... truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Man, Elfman, will protect Fairy Tail with his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Salut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An Element 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Elfman can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:25.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's a Fairy Tail Wizard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I detest girls like this who try to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Witness your friend's final moments as I crush her slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got to hurry and stop that giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Gray... Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:11.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sol! Please call me Monsieur Sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing. I'll force you to tell me how to stop this giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:23.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Just your right arm? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the rumors are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your blabbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:35.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have a little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sable Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roche Concerto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Salut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really creep me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three nons and you're in quite a sad state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand me, Monster Sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's way stronger than he looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You failed at a complete body takeover and went out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Beast Arm Iron Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:28.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But as you were stepping on me previously, I read the gap in your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:34.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a precious little sister of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she might be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how {\i1}rude{\i0} of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:44.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's buried in the cold, dark ground, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do such a cruel thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan, my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be deceived... I've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:13.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you made a debacle of a full body Take Over, and you lost control?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what you did the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Elf-niichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't try to do what you can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your magical power has weakened considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Man, then fight me fair and square, fist to fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm a man, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let that pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not from someone with no right to question the manliness of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:56.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash like you who killed his own little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plâtre Sonate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So she is your elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means she was once the feared Devil, Mirajane-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost so much of her magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity! And who could be to blame for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is being punished for attempting to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long until she is crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let my sister go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will lose your elder sister right before your eyes, just like the younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:59.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is because you are an impotent wizard who does nothing but spout bluffs about manliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a gentleman, I cannot forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you eternal suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Magic, Merci la Vie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will become one with the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and continue to wander for eternity inside your own unpleasant memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:49.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, Elf-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault... It's my fault my parakeet died!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Elf-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:02.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every living thing dies sometime, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All living things... die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as you remember it, that bird will always live on inside your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you understand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lisanna... You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu was really mean! He ate all my fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lisanna, we got a job to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we just come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an S-class, too! We'll back Sis up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of job is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading toward the king of monsters, "The Beast."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you wanna come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be good experience for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I'm against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man should protect his family on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, don't be so stuffy! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least, take Natsu with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, hang in there! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I evacuated all the people in the town... But what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:20.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman attempted to protect me, and he tried a Take Over on The Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However its magical power was too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman's lost his reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to Elf-niichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't come to his senses soon, he'll be taken by The Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your little sister, Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget Mira-nee, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:58.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that you'd forget us, right Elf-niichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:03.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we both love you very much, Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go home, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every living thing dies sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening back then, Nee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna will live on forever in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So... We're going to keep on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Lisanna's sake, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:23.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... lose you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's about time for the finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:42.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I vowed never to see my sister's tears again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are ya' crying for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Elfman! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that made her cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:59.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible! You are not capable of doing a full body Take Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:11.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:15.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A full body Take Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:30.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:40.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:52.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:57.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:03.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:10.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:21.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:30.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:34.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:37.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:41.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:45.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:54.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Happy... It seems like it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Our guild's full of holes right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many holes, there's no lack of leaks in the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:10.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's more like actual rain than leaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got an air of rickety ancient ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: A Flower Blooms in the Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better fix it quick before we catch colds!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.26,0:24:22.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of like a giant shower though... Fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You take positive thinking too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
